import React,{useState} from 'react' import Nav from '../../../components/layout' import Link from 'next/link' import {useRouter} from 'next/router' const Index = ()=>{ const [value,setValue] = useState(null) const router = useRouter() const {tid} = router.query fetch(`https://test.ipdb.io/api/v1/assets/?search=${tid}`) .then((response)=>response.json()) .then((r)=>setValue(r[0].data.input)) return( <>


Record
  • Blood Pressure: {value && value.bp}
  • Diabetics: {value && value.diabetics}
  • Smoke ?: {value && value.smoke}
) } export default Index
